features: 【Multifunctional Tablet for Kids and Adults】- This is not just a tablet but a multi-functional gadget that serves both kids and adults. It comes pre-installed with Google Kids Space offering 10,000 relevant e-books, YouTube Kids, and age-appropriate apps and games. Adults have complete access to Google services. Guaranteed educational and fun for tech-savvy kids and adults.

【Powerful Performance】- Brace yourself for a surprisingly powerful performance from our Kids Tablet. Running on an advanced Android 13.0 OS, with a fast 2.0GHz OCta-core CPU, an 8GB RAM and 128GB ROM for speedy multitasking. It also supports Wifi 6.0, 2.4G&5G dual Wifi, and Bluetooth 5.0 GPS, and can hold up to 2TB expandable storage with microSD (not include), perfect for intensive personal and educational usage alike.

【Easy-to-use Parental Control】 - Pre-installed Google Family Link app makes it easy to have parental control and it is very easy to use too. You can create and customize profiles for kids’ accounts, hand-pick content for your kids, limit usage time per day, and ensure they are browsing safe websites. The security settings can also be adjusted to be more tailored as your child grows.

【Impressive Display and Camera】- The 10.1" IPS 1920x1200 Eye Protection HD Touch Screen is designed to deliver bright and vivid graphics, making it the perfect display for gaming and educational purposes. Plus, with a 5MP front and a 13MP rear camera, you're getting high-quality imaging that's ideal for preserving precious memories and making crystal clear video calls. It's all about providing a comprehensive visual and interactive experience with our top-tier display and camera features.

【8000mAh Long-Lasting Battery and Warranty】- With a powerful 8000mAh battery, the tablet guarantees 15-20 hours of usage time. This ensures uninterrupted learning or browsing experience. Also, it is backed by a 2-year warranty and lifetime customer service, ensuring that any product issues are covered and providing peace of mind to users.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars awesome performance and really nice display
reviews.reviewText: this kids tablet is surprisingly quick and easy to use. the included storage is more than enough for most people but it is expandable via micro sd. the screen is bright enough to use as a media player on long car trips. the tablet comes with the latest android version and is speedy and responsive even with multiple tabs open and apps running.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Kids tablet? Not quite...
reviews.reviewText: Got this as a back-up to my youngest actual kid tablet and was highly amazed when I opened it and it turned out to be an actual tablet running Android 13. The operating system is rather powerful, not the strongest on the market, but you can easily run games like Asphalt, ROBLOX or Minecraft without lagging.The HDD can be expanded to 1TB, which is pretty insane for a handheld device.Amazing cameras, one in 8MP, the other 13MP.Get a case for this bad boy, pronto!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Decent specs and a great case
reviews.reviewText: The best part of this is the case. I dare not say anything is kid proof, but this case withstands quite a bit of rough use while keeping the tablet is good condition. The specs are average and on par with lower cost tablets, but as a package one time buy it is competitive.Overall, we are very happy with the performance of this tablet.
